That would be coherent with "bootstrap" path to have a kernel dir relative to the config file where it is declared.

```php
    protected static function getKernelClass()
    {
        $dir = static::getPhpUnitXmlDir();
        if (isset($_SERVER['KERNEL_DIR'])) {
            $dir = realpath($dir . '/' . $_SERVER['KERNEL_DIR']) ?: $_SERVER['KERNEL_DIR'];
        }
        ...
    }
```

